===Etymology===
From ''[[Lycopdium]]'' (a genus) + [[-phyta]]

===Proper noun===
'''Lycopodiophyta'''

#{{botany}}: A [[botanical name]] for a [[taxon]] within [[kingdom]] [[Plantae]] that includes the [[clubmoss]]es, [[spikemoss]]es, and [[quillwort]]s. The taxon is traditionally given the [[rank]] of a [[division]].

